{"tid":1559143,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"<快手>商人遭10漢持「伸縮警棍」入屋毆劫  失275萬涉生意糾紛","createTime":"2019-09-10T16:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T07:04:54.000Z","uid":227801,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c8cccda55009f07fbe3895acce7abe33610c8d77","tid":1559143,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:37:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190910/60027980\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F60027980&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRemt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=2f9f7d4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F60027980&h=9b75940d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190910/60027980</a><br />\n旺角亞皆老街一單位，凌晨零時許，一名48歲姓余女子報案，指有10多人入屋，當中有人持伸縮警棍，打傷其34歲姓張丈夫後，搶去約275萬元現金後往旺角道方向逃去。救護員到場將該男事主送院，他頭及手受傷，警方正調查案件。<br />\n據悉，男事主在內地從事貿易生意，事件疑涉及生意糾紛。凌晨時分，其中一名相識男子到訪，事主打開門後，逾10人一擁而入，毆打及威脅事主打開夾萬，搶走約275萬元逃去。案件暫列行劫，交由旺角警區刑事調查隊第五隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n警方呼籲市民如目擊上述案件或就案件有資料提供，可致電3661 8765與調查人員聯絡。<br />\n雖然近日內地禁止一系列防具及武器運送到香港，不過《蘋果》發現不法之徒仍能輕易從內地購入伸縮警棍。淘寶購物網有售賣各式伸縮警棍，其中一款「美國悍馬」，普通版只售人民幣38元（約港幣43元），而升級版則售人民幣64元（約港幣70元），購買伸縮警棍更送鋒利彎刀、破窗器等用品。賣家更聲稱伸縮警棍可以輕易扑碎磚頭，更可以砸彎士巴拿，連遭汽車輾過亦毫無損傷。"},{"pid":"63a5b5c854213d009b44496495356909543aae3d","tid":1559143,"uid":9542,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:38:41.000Z","msg":"係咪休班警做"},{"pid":"d082f587739b5d95853f3c42b5c463ea9d9002ce","tid":1559143,"uid":761,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:38:58.000Z","msg":"有種罪犯叫休班警"},{"pid":"1b8c6880c4463377e55d666cde351ed6cdc20143","tid":1559143,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:39:37.000Z","msg":"謝sir咁想同人傾計，我地所有人都奉陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請即參與：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>#wtsappforhk campaign (#eye4hk 2.0) </strong></span><br />\n有twitter既快啲retweet，無twitter既而家開番個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">本地線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 將警暴，藍絲，官員，議員罪證狂推比警察<br />\n<br />\n2. 為左令每一個負責mon住既阿sir都不愁寂莫，每個人睇番自己生日日子既最後一位數字，揀下表有同樣最尾位數字既電話<br />\n<br />\n3. 有關如何保護自己，請搜尋「太空」等相關字眼<br />\n<br />\n5566 9500<br />\n5566 9501<br />\n5566 9502<br />\n5566 9503<br />\n5566 9504<br />\n5566 9505<br />\n5566 9506<br />\n5566 9507<br />\n5566 9508<br />\n5566 9509<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n1. retweet手足既呢條tweet, 記住comment加#wtsappforhk<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRemt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=e17409ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&h=44f2ff93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 如果你選擇將10個電話重新打一次出黎，記得加+852<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1. 成本低<br />\n2. 可以迫大家儲下唔同角度文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n1. 本地線唔會要大家post番個舉報cap圖出黎，少左第二次marketing機會 (which is fine)<br />\n2. 外國人參與國際線程度成疑，但我覺得以campaign之名，行宣傳之實。就咁講#chinazi，#culturalrevolution，老實講有d悶。"},{"pid":"63d0a7acb8cb7b1a42ec16c4888fe6a18b6912cc","tid":1559143,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:39:55.000Z","msg":"蘋果最尾仲要幫佢地兜<br />\n<br />\n買到=/=運到呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52957a